net.sourceforge.jwebunit.api

Interface IElement

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    HtmlUnitElementImpl, WebDriverElementImpl

    public interface IElement
    A wrapper around elements so we can access their properties directly, without requiring either direct access to the testing engine DOM, or implementing every permutation of assert test.
    Author:
    jmwright

      • setTextContent

        void setTextContent(String value)
        Set the text content on this element. Note that if you are trying to set the value of an <input> input, you should use setAttribute("value") instead. This also sets the text content of a <textarea> element.
        Parameters:
        value - the new inner text content of this element
